      "key": "228.0",
      "line_index": 228,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c863802",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "うっ……そ、そろそろ……イク……ぞ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "231.0",
      "line_index": 231,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8ae46e19",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "また限界に近づいた俺はあらかじめシーシャにそう告げる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
